         <div>
            <entry xml:id="L9c6d415bc0ad41fca8498aa2a287de1d" n="7264">
               <form>
                  <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዕዝል</foreign>
               <rs type="root"/>
                    </form>
               <sense xml:lang="la" source="#dillmann" xml:id="Dmain"> (etiam <foreign xml:lang="gez">እዝል፡</foreign>) <gramGrp> <pos expand="Substantivum">subst.</pos> </gramGrp>, <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la">
                            <quote> unus e tribus cantandi modis </quote>
                        </cit>, qui in decantandis hymnis sacris vel ecclesiasticis usitati sunt (distinguuntur enim <foreign xml:lang="gez">፫ ዜማ፡ ዘውእቱ፡ ግዕዝ፡ ወዕዝል፡ ወአራራይ፡</foreign> <ref cRef="Sx. Genb." loc="11">Sx. Genb. 11</ref>); accuratior ejus descriptio desideratur; Villoteau in Description de l’Égypte tom. XIV ait: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ግዕዝ፡</foreign> pour les jours de férie; <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዕዝል፡</foreign> pour les jours de jeûne et de carême, pour les veilles de fêtes et pour les cérémonies funèbres; <foreign xml:lang="gez">አራራይ፡</foreign> aux principales fêtes de l’année. (E qua descriptione, comparatis nominum <foreign xml:lang="gez">ግዕዝ፡</foreign> et <foreign xml:lang="gez">አራራይ፡</foreign> significationibus, si quid conjicere licet, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዕዝል፡</foreign> ad <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la">
                            <quote> vocem </quote>
                        </cit> cantantium <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la">
                            <quote> demissam </quote>
                        </cit> et <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la">
                            <quote> compressam </quote>
                        </cit>[<foreign xml:lang="ar">ذَلَّ</foreign>? <foreign xml:lang="ar">عُزْلٌ</foreign>?] spectare videtur). Deinde etiam <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la">
                            <quote> hymnus </quote>
                        </cit> <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la">
                            <quote> hoc modo cantandus </quote>
                        </cit> <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዕዝል፡</foreign> nominatur. Crebro occurrit in Hymnologiis et libris liturgicis, ut: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዕዝል፡ ዘነግህ፡</foreign> Deg.; <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዕዝል፡ ዘእግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡</foreign> Deg.; <foreign xml:lang="gez">ህየንተ፡ ዕዝል፡ ዘነግህ፡ ግዕዝ፡</foreign> Deg.; <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዕዝል፡ ዘሙታን፡</foreign> Deg.; <ref cRef="Genz." loc="13 ">Genz. f. 13 </ref>(<lbl expand="videas">vid. sub</lbl> <foreign xml:lang="gez">መወድስ፡</foreign>); <foreign xml:lang="gez">ትብል፡ በዜማ፡ ዕዝል፡ ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡ ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡ ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡</foreign> <ref cRef="Genz." loc="101">Genz. f. 101</ref>; Cod. Mus. Brit. LIV, n. 7; al. </sense>
               
